ommunity groups to promote prevention and fire and co safety and we help our distributors through pointofpurchase sales tools and special seasonal promotions we are totally committed to serving our customers from you  the professionals who install our products  to the families who count on them we are proud of the products we make and welcome the opportunity to serve all our customers together      brk brands inc all rights reserved used under license by the first alert trust home  company profile  newspress  special announcements  contact us  special needs  global sites  legalprivacy home contact us search view catalog products faqstroubleshooting register your products hardwired battery plugin fire extinguishers other safety products security cameras new construction mro professionals oems diy contractor installed brk professionals new construction » products hardwired smoke alarms co alarms smokeco combo alarms heat alarms onelink alarms misc battery smoke alarms co alarms smokeco combo alarms onelink alarms plugin co alarms explosive gasco combo alarms fire extinguishers traditional tundra other safety products safety ladders motion sensors adaptor plugs misc security cameras wired cameras wireless cameras camera accessories » downloads logos catalog products listing cards cross reference listing other » cross reference list » codes » legislation map » listing cards mro professionals oems other links » company profile » rep locator » customer service numbers » news  press » become a distributor products » hardwired » smoke alarm » co alarm » smokeco combo alarm » heat alarm » onelink alarm » misc » battery » smoke alarm » co alarm » smokeco combo alarm » onelink alarm » plugin » co alarm » explosive gasco combo alarm » fire extinguisher » traditional » tundra » other safety products » safety ladder » motion sensor » adaptor plug » misc » security cameras » wired cameras » wireless cameras » camera accessories  brk brands inc all rights reserved used under licens