ed an assortment of manufacturing companies that produce railroad tank cars shopping carts plumbing pipes metal fasteners wiring and water treatment products used in residential construction on october   berkshire hathaway automotive an autodealership subsidiary was created through the acquisition of van tuyl group the remaining largest auto dealer in the nation and independentlyowned up to that date and it is the fifth largest with ownership of  dealerships and revenues of  billion on november   berkshire hathaway announced that it would acquire duracell from procter  gamble for  billion in an allstock deal finance and financial productsedit berkshire acquired clayton homes a maker of modular homes storage trailers chassis intermodal piggyback trailers and domestic containers claytons finance business loans to manufactured home owners earned  million down from  million in  loan losses remain  up from  investmentsedit as well as owning companies outright berkshire maintains a concentrated portfolio of equities and investments which has historically been managed by warren buffett since  todd combs and ted weschler also work alongside buffett in managing investments in the  letter to shareholders warren revealed that each of them independently manages greater than  billion on behalf of berkshire buffett has spoken very highly of both in public interviews and in the  letter to shareholders he described hiring them both as one of my best moves as of march   of berkshires equity securities are concentrated in five companies american express company   billion apple inc   billion the cocacola company   billion international business machines corporation “ibm”   billion and wells fargo  company   billion at the peak of the financial crisis in september  berkshire invested  billion in preferred stock in goldman sachs to provide it with a source of funding when capital markets had become constrained the preferred stock yielded an annual interest rate of  earning berkshire  mi